#https://man.archlinux.org/man/zathurarc.5

# Enable copy to clipboard
set selection-clipboard clipboard

## Visuals
set window-height 1400
set window-width 1500
set guioptions shv
set font "monospace normal 15"

## Control
map d scroll half-down
map u scroll half-up
map <C-k> zoom in
map <C-j> zoom out
map h navigate previous
map l navigate next

